{"tid":2156131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解陳健民 Youtube 咁少人睇？","createTime":"2020-08-14T08:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:10:39.000Z","uid":172061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ad6b866fb8047366334c0babffafa8cc2a7d76","tid":2156131,"uid":172061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PkInPFFoZ-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPkInPFFoZ-c&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=c4da3fea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PkInPFFoZ-c</a><br />\n<br />\n話晒佢都係大學教授，因為場運動坐監連教席都辭埋，而家拍 YouTube 得幾千 subscription，每條片得咁幾千 view，我覺得都好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好奇問下大家點解，係咪因為以前行過入中聯辦所以大家都歸類佢做左膠？<br />\n<br />\n但我又覺得好多左膠一路走來都有改變既，無以前咁左膠，雖則大家未必認同互相一啲睇法做法，路線不盡相同，但都係坐埋一條船，起碼當支持下個黃 Youtuber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係覺得一個教授坐完出來做 Youtube 得咁少 view 有啲可惜，有感而發。"},{"pid":"d1c3df94e83aa6c76dc423ee86beae090ebcedae","tid":2156131,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"因為我根本唔知原來佢有個channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ba6b980d446b1712b97f93ee736c39cd2be936","tid":2156131,"uid":172061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c3df94e83aa6c76dc423ee86beae090ebcedae","tid":2156131,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"因為我根本唔知原來佢有個channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"咁發揮下香港人撐蘋果既精神入去訂閱下個 channel 當支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(利申：有時聽佢講野令我諗起以前返大學聽 Lecture，雖然係無沈旭輝教授講野咁快板，但都係有質素既野，希望多啲人聽下)"}]}